{"tid":1726312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"催淚彈射中頭15歲傅同學仍昏迷命危","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T01:54:33.000Z","uid":290993,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"43a39c3ee3aa75e48b1afcdf260000504dc8be03","tid":1726312,"uid":290993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"已經無人講呢單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n昏迷指數3即係同周同學之前一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">集氣</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%84%E4%B8%AD%E9%A0%AD-%E5%82%85%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E5%91%BD%E5%8D%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2582%2585%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%258D%25B1%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=099c77b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2582%2585%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E5%2591%25BD%25E5%258D%25B1%2F&h=32af59de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%96%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%84%E4%B8%AD%E9%A0%AD-%E5%82%85%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E5%91%BD%E5%8D%B1/</a><br />\n<br />\n前晚（13日）有示威者在多區堵路，其中在天水圍警署外有大批市民聚集，15 歲的傅同學疑被催淚彈射中頭，顱骨骨折。消息人士指，傅同學手術紀錄為槍傷，現時情況仍然危殆，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏迷指數只有3分，屬最低分</span></span></strong>，「即係眼無張開、插喉、對痛楚無知覺反應。」<br />\n<br />\n當時在現場為傅同學急救的何先生接受《立場新聞》訪問時透露，當時傅同學頭頂正中間偏右後流血，右腿大髀上方亦有懷疑被催淚彈射中、3 至 4 級燒傷的痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n傅同學的母親數年前因胃癌離世，父親在三年前亦患病離世，自此便與哥哥相依為命。"},{"pid":"20018d480b4fbf60d66f7885aae11201c0cf494a","tid":1726312,"uid":332635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519bf7581851a7c1f39eac07771d84f4a94c8b2","tid":1726312,"uid":279038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6205aac7839477d1b0ced7a6e628f98b561434","tid":1726312,"uid":279038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"一定要冇事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0ea9aafec0465d5584e122c45a04e0e16f7793","tid":1726312,"uid":246158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm